  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A systematic open-label prospective pilot study to assess aripirazole for acute bipolar
      depression, with a secondary assessment of longer-term mood stabilization.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study is 6 weeks long with 7 clinical visits.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
