  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  DSM-IV diagnosis of bipolar disorder, any subtype; MADRS &gt;16; MRS &lt; 10; not currently
             taking other mood stabilizers; women of reproductive potential must use an acceptable
             method of birth control

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Current substance abuse within past month; serious unstable medical condition; active
             suicidal ideation; pregnant, trying to become pregnant, or nursing; intent to continue
             or initiate herbal preparations
      </textblock>
